  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    A brief outline of an Architectural Review Record:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;blockquote style=&quot;MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>&#xD;
    &lt;h4>&#xD;
        1. Executive Summary&#xD;
    &lt;/h4>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        An executive summary of the review â€” required if the review is large or significant.&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;h4>&#xD;
        2. Goals and Objectives&#xD;
    &lt;/h4>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        List the work products that will be the subject of this review and the coverage (all, business level, network&#xD;
        aspect, etc.).&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;h4>&#xD;
        3. Scope &amp;amp; Level&#xD;
    &lt;/h4>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        Identify the scope of the review and the review level (see: &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithType&quot;&#xD;
        href=&quot;./../../../UAM/guidances/guidelines/uam_architecture_review_51A5B1E7.html&quot;&#xD;
        guid=&quot;_BdyOIFEvEeOcVJX_gvTjyg&quot;>Guideline: Architecture Review&lt;/a>).&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;h4>&#xD;
        4. Review Participants&#xD;
    &lt;/h4>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        List the individuals who will participate in the review and their roles during the meeting; for example, moderator,&#xD;
        note-taker, reviewer, author.&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;h4>&#xD;
        5.&amp;nbsp;Overall Architecture&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
    &lt;/h4>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        Identify the high-level architectural concerns regarding areas such as structure, patterns, organization of models,&#xD;
        interfaces, etc.&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;h4>&#xD;
        6.&amp;nbsp;Specific Architecture Aspects&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
    &lt;/h4>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        Define the specific concerns under various categories such as as application, information or operational&#xD;
        architectures, security, integration and interfaces, technology, etc.&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;h4>&#xD;
        7.&amp;nbsp;Key Findings&amp;nbsp;&amp;amp; Actions&#xD;
    &lt;/h4>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        List the key findings identified during the review.&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;/blockquote>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Various formats are provided below: Microsoft Word (.dotx and .dot), PDF (.pdf) and Open XML Paper Specification&#xD;
    (.xps).&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
